.Dd May 17, 2026
.Dt STEALTHSTREAMTERMINAL 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm stealthstreamterminal
.Nd DOOMSDAY terminal module
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is the named DOOMSDAY module for the customized
.Xr st 1
terminal build. It installs the terminal binary, desktop entry, man page, and
terminfo data from the StealthStreamTerminal repository.
.Sh INSTALL
.Dl \&./install.sh --sst
.Sh INSTALLED COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width "st"
.It Nm st
Terminal emulator executable.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr doomsday-system 1 ,
.Xr st 1
